## ⭐ 眼科

picture_counter_4 A lone, dark-clad figure stands on a narrow, rocky cliff edge, facing a vast, mist-filled canyon. A single, slender waterfall cascades down the far cliff, disappearing into the haze. The scene is rendered in muted blues and grays, with soft, diffused light suggesting early morning or twilight, emphasizing solitude and scale.

- 位置： 楼西区 4
- 路线：门诊大厅乘 2 号电梯至 4 楼，出电梯右转眼科专区


## 科室简介

眼科为医院重点建设科室之一，拥有完善的诊疗体系与专业设备，长期承担区域医疗服务任务。


